pra criar
npx create-next-app nome

pra rodar
yarn dev

instalar typescript
yarn add typescript @types/react @types/node -D


add sass
yarn add sass


add extensao cssmodules e sass
yarn add sass


icones
yarn add react-icons



axios pra usar json externo, nookies pra configurar cookies e jwt-decode pra decodificar o jwt
yarn add axios nookies jwt-decode


personalizar alertas
https://fkhadra.github.io/react-toastify/installation
yarn add react-toastify